reviews.review:
Ever get that premonition? that somethings lurking around the corner, behind a bush, or is just lurking in the dark waiting for you? Well do you love that feeling? Then this game is great for you! a willed survivor ready to avoid death at all costs.

On the other hand do you like the hunger to strike down? The adrenaline of the chase? Then the killer side is what you want! perk yourself to be the most annoying or deadly killer the campfire has ever seen. remember they can hide and try but you'll never let them see daylight~

honestly a fun game ;3;
